Repository Licensing

This repository contains multiple licensing scopes:

- ZeroTierOne upstream source code is not vendored in this repository. It is
  downloaded from https://github.com/zerotier/ZeroTierOne and remains under the
  upstream ZeroTierOne license.
- patches/openbsd-managed-ip-multicast-subscriptions.patch modifies
  ZeroTierOne source files that are licensed under the Mozilla Public License
  2.0. The patch is therefore distributed under MPL-2.0.
- install.sh, README.md, .gitignore, and repository-local documentation are
  distributed under the MIT License below.

Credit notices must be preserved:

- ZeroTier, Inc. and the ZeroTierOne project: https://github.com/zerotier/ZeroTierOne
- OpenBSD installer and multicast subscription patch: itinfra7 from GitHub

